metadata.name: 2023 Volume 1 - The Year of Yuga
metadata.description:
Welcome to 2023, the Year of Yuga!  Yuga Labs closed out 2022 with a bang, teasing out future utility for the Yacht Club and The Otherside that sent shock waves through the community and NFT market as a whole.  There's no denying the hype surrounding what comes next, and we fully believe this year will be defined by the execution of the Yuga Labs team.  

Volume 1 represents the key to all BoringStone 2023 cover drops as it will be burnable for any future volumes.  How many drops are expected this year?  Your guess is as good as ours.
